<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Platforma on RailTech</title><link>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/tags/platforma/</link><description>Recent content in Platforma on RailTech</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>uz</language><atom:link href="https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/tags/platforma/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>RailTech B2B raqamli platformasi</title><link>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/projects/b2b-platform/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/projects/b2b-platform/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Loyiha haqida
 &lt;div id="loyiha-haqida" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#loyiha-haqida" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2024-yilda «RailTech» o&amp;rsquo;z faoliyatini raqamlashtirish va hamkorlar uchun qulay raqamli muhit yaratish maqsadida B2B platformani ishlab chiqdi va ishga tushirdi.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Vazifa
 &lt;div id="vazifa" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#vazifa" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Temir yo&amp;rsquo;l uskunalarini xarid qilish jarayonini soddalashtiruvchi, shaffof va samarali qiluvchi raqamli platforma yaratish.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Platforma modullari
 &lt;div id="platforma-modullari" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#platforma-modullari" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Katalog&lt;/strong&gt; — 500+ mahsulotning batafsil texnik tavsifnomalari bilan raqamli katalogi&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TT Kalkulyator&lt;/strong&gt; — narxlarni avtomatik hisoblash va tijorat takliflarini shakllantirish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bitimlar&lt;/strong&gt; — buyurtmalar va shartnomalarni boshqarish tizimi&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shaxsiy kabinet&lt;/strong&gt; — hamkorlar uchun boshqaruv paneli&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart Import&lt;/strong&gt; — import operatsiyalarini boshqarish moduli&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Admin panel&lt;/strong&gt; — platforma boshqaruvi uchun administrator paneli&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Natijalar
 &lt;div id="natijalar" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#natijalar" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Platforma muvaffaqiyatli ishga tushirildi va 120 dan ortiq hamkor tomonidan faol foydalanilmoqda. Buyurtma berish vaqti o&amp;rsquo;rtacha 60% ga qisqardi, hujjat aylanmasi to&amp;rsquo;liq raqamlashtirildi.&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/projects/b2b-platform/featured.jpg"/></item></channel></rss>